1. Which of the following is true about class inheritance?

a)Class inheritance lets you reuse code and makes your program easier to maintain.

b)Properties and functions of the parent class(es) are available to the child class.

c)You can define additional properties and functions that are specific to subclasses.

d)You can override parent class members in subclasses.

e)All of the above


