a)They can be extended by subclasses and implementations can be provided for abstract members of the class.

b)They have an implementation for all of their properties and functions.

c)They may have abstract properties or abstract functions.

d)They can be instantiated.

e)They are not fully implemented and cannot be instantiated.

f)They need to be marked with the open keyword to be extended

